        <h2>WEDDINGS:</h2>
        <h3>GARHWALI WEDDING:</h3>
        <p>
            Garhwali weddings are simple yet vibrant, rooted in local traditions and customs. Key rituals include Ganesh Puja, Kanyadaan, and Phera, with the bride wearing a traditional Pichora. Folk songs and dances add charm to the celebration, reflecting the culture of the Garhwal region.  
        </p>
